ext_description.note:
This schema is upward compatible, for their common scope areas, with ISO 10303-214:2003, with the following exceptions:


the concept of product_class has a single mapping in the present application module, onto the entity product_class;

the concept of product_identification is only mapped in the present application module, onto the entities product_identification and product_specification;

the concept of general_classification defined in the ARM of ISO 10303-214:2003 has a single mapping in the present application module, onto the entity characterized_class;

the concept of physical_model is mapped onto a subtype of product_definition and not of product_definition_with_associated_documents.
